{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"651","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"因應疫情 勞動部專案勞檢全面延後","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '>2020-03-10 16:50 </span><span style='font-family: '>聯合報<span lang='EN-US'> / </span>記者葉冠妤／台北即時報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8B%9E%E5%8B%95%E9%83%A8.JPG' style='width: 800px; height: 585px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>勞動部表示，受疫情影響，專案勞動檢查將延後舉辦。聯合報系資料照片／記者葉冠妤攝影</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>新冠肺炎疫情延燒，勞動部職安署署長鄒子廉今表示，受疫情影響，專案勞動檢查將延後舉辦。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>勞動部去年從公共安全、弱勢扶助、知識密集、常態違規及社會關注等面向，專案勞檢<span lang='EN-US'>8000</span>家事業單位，鄒子廉表示，每年約<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月左右啟動專案勞檢，但今年受疫情影響，專案勞檢延期，後續視疫情發展再盤點規畫。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>鄒子廉說，過去會針對醫療院所進行專案勞檢，今年考量特殊情況，以防疫為重，會暫緩醫護人員的勞檢，但職安署仍舊會提醒醫療院所須注意醫護人員過勞問題。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>此外，鄒子廉說，針對中小企業的法遵訪視計畫仍照常；勞工申訴案件若成案，職安署也會積極查處，不會停擺，但他強調，若申訴案涉及如高風險的醫療院所，為尊重疫情指揮中心的指揮權，會跟指揮中心報備討論。</span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://udn.com/news/story/7238/4403771</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-03-11","clk_count":"189"}},"__N_SSG":true}